Prionacalus simonsi

; Monné and Giesbert 1994: 15 (checklist); 
Monné 1995: 61
(catalogue), 2006: 83 (catalogue); 
Di Iorio 2003: 3
(distribution); Monné and Hovore 2005: 19 (checklist), 2006: 18 (checklist); 
